(13, 'tr', 'Ortaklarımız', '<p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li> <a href="http://www.amazee.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Amazee </strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Amazee&quot;''de &uuml;yeler &quot;Social Collaboration&quot; sayesinde hedeflerini ger&ccedil;ekleştirebiliyorlar. Amazee b&uuml;y&uuml;k projeler i&ccedil;in &uuml;&ccedil;retsiz bir plattformdur.</li></ul><blockquote> <img src="/img/comm_icons/amazee.jpg" border="0" alt="amazee-logo" width="90" height="31" /></blockquote><ul><li> <a href="http://www.bankingclub.de/" target="_blank"><strong>BankingCLUB</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Bankingclub&quot; banka &ccedil;al&iota;şanlar&iota; i&ccedil;in uygun bir plattformdur. Bankingclub en b&uuml;y&uuml;k alman branş ve ekonomi kul&uuml;plerinden biridir. </li></ul><blockquote><div align="left"><a href="http://www.bankingclub.de" title="Bankingclub - Networking unter Gleichgesinnten"><img src="/img/comm_icons/bankingclub.jpg" border="0" alt="bankingclub-logo" width="99" height="30" /> </a></div></blockquote> <ul><li> <a href="http://www.dozentenscout.de/" target="_blank"><strong>DozentenScout</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Dozentenscout&quot;''da &ccedil;al&iota;şt&iota;r&iota;c&iota;lar ve dan&iota;şmanlar sipariş bulabiliyorlar ve kendi seminerlerini sunabiliyorlar. Dozentenscout Almanyada en b&uuml;y&uuml;k Online-&ccedil;al&iota;şt&iota;r&iota;c&iota;-community''lerinden biridir.</li></ul><blockquote> <img src="/img/comm_icons/dobo.jpg" border="0" alt="dozenten-boerse-logo" /><br /></blockquote><ul><li> <a href="http://www.edelight.de/" target="_blank"><strong>edelight</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;edelight&quot;da her vesile i&ccedil;in  hediye bulabilirsiniz. Edelight Almanyan&iota;n, sadece hediyeyle ilgilenen, ilk shopping- ve hediye-portal&iota;.  </li></ul><blockquote><a href="http://www.edelight.de" title="edelight - Products you love."><img src="/img/comm_icons/edelight_logo.png" border="0" alt="edelight-logo" /></a></blockquote> <ul><li> <a href="http://www.euni.de/" target="_blank"><strong>eUNI</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;euni.de&quot; &uuml;niversite-&ouml;ğrencileri, profes&ouml;rler ve do&ccedil;entler i&ccedil;in bir plattformdur. eUni.de d&uuml;nyan&iota;n &ouml;nde gelen akademik kariyer netw&ouml;rklerinden biridir.  </li></ul><blockquote><a href="http://www.euni.de" title="eUni - the academic career network"><img src="/img/comm_icons/eUni.jpg" border="0" alt="eUni-logo" /></a></blockquote> <ul><li> <a href="http://www.familyone.de/" target="_blank"><strong>Family One</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;FamilyOne&quot;da aileni ve arkadaşlar&iota;n&iota; online yaşam&iota;na ekliyorsun. FamilyOne aileler  i&ccedil;in &ouml;zel bir SocialNetw&ouml;rk'' dur.                            </li></ul><blockquote><a href="http://www.familyone.de" title="FamilyOne - Teilen Sie Ihr Leben online mit Familie und Freunden"><img src="/img/comm_icons/familyone.jpg" border="0" alt="familyone-logo" width="100" height="32" /></a></blockquote><ul><li> <a href="http://www.freelancer1.de/" target="_blank"><strong>freelancer1</strong></a></li></ul><blockquote> Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Freelancer1&quot;de serbest iş&ccedil;iler kontak kurabiliyor ve iş bulabiliyorlar. Her serbest &ccedil;al&iota;şanlar i&ccedil;in bir mecburiyet!</blockquote><blockquote><a href="http://www.freelancer1.de" title="freelancer1 - Die Boerse fuer Freiberufler"><img src="/img/comm_icons/flan.jpg" border="0" alt="freelancer1-logo" /></a></blockquote><ul><li> <a href="http://grafiker.de" target="_blank"><strong>Grafiker.de</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Grafiker.de&quot; grafik&ccedil;iler, programc&iota;lar ve fotoğraf&ccedil;&iota;lar  i&ccedil;in interaktiv bir plattformdur.</li></ul><blockquote><a href="http://www.sixgroups.de" title="sixgroups - Kennst Du Deine Community?"><img src="/img/comm_icons/grafiker_logo.png" border="0" alt="sixgroups-logo" /></a></blockquote> <ul><li> <a href="http://www.golfnetworkclub.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Golf Network Club</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;GolfNetworkClub&quot; b&uuml;t&uuml;n d&uuml;nyadaki golfcular i&ccedil;in bir buluşma noktas&iota;d&iota;r. GolfNetworkClub b&uuml;t&uuml;n d&uuml;nyadaki golfcular&iota; biraraya topluyup, organizasyonlarda &ouml;zel avantajlar sunuyor.</li></ul><blockquote> <a href="http://www.golfnetworkclub.com/" title="GolfNetworkClub - The international golf community"><img src="/img/comm_icons/golf.jpg" border="0" alt="golfnetworkclub-logo" /></a></blockquote> <ul><li> <a href="http://www.imedo.de/" target="_blank"><strong>Imedo</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;imedo&quot;''da sağl&iota;kla ilgili sorular&iota;n&iota;z&iota; cevaplandirabilir, doktorlardan tavsiye alabilir ve uygun terapi bulabilrsiniz. Imedo, tavsiyeleri ile, &ccedil;ok iyi bir sağl&iota;k-portal&iota;d&iota;r.</li></ul><blockquote><div> <a href="http://www.imedo.de" title="imedo - gemeinsam gesund"><img src="/img/comm_icons/imedo.jpg" border="0" alt="imedo-logo" /></a></div></blockquote> <ul><li> <a href="http://jajah.com" target="_blank"><strong>Jajah</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Jajah&quot; ile internet sayesinde sabit hatta &uuml;&ccedil;retsiz konuşabiliyorsunuz. Biz bunu beğendiğimiz i&ccedil;in, communipedia''ya ekledik.</li></ul><blockquote><a href="http://www.sixgroups.de" title="sixgroups - Kennst Du Deine Community?"><img src="/img/comm_icons/jajah_logo.png" border="0" alt="sixgroups-logo" width="53" height="30" /></a></blockquote> <ul><li> <a href="http://de.jimdo.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Jimdo</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Jimdo&quot; ile &uuml;yeler kendi internet sayfalar&iota;n&iota; h&iota;zl&iota; ve kolay &uuml;retebiliyor ve kendilerini b&uuml;t&uuml;n d&uuml;nyada yaz&iota;larla ve resimlerle sunma imkan&iota; buluyorlar.  </li></ul><blockquote><a href="http://www.jimdo.de" title="jimdo - pages to the people"><img src="/img/comm_icons/jimdo.jpg" border="0" alt="jimdo-logo" /></a></blockquote><ul><li> <a href="http://www.joinr.de/" target="_blank"><strong>Joinr</strong></a> </li></ul><blockquote>Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;JoinR&quot; ile Social-Networking kolaylaş&iota;yor. Internette &uuml;&ccedil;retsiz kendi yerini &uuml;retip, arkadaşlar&iota;nla paylaşabilirsin.</blockquote><blockquote><a href="http://www.joinr.de" title="joinr - Deine Webseite - Deine Freunde"><img src="/img/comm_icons/joinr.jpg" border="0" alt="join-logo" /></a></blockquote> <ul><li> <a href="http://www.marketing-boerse.de/Experten/details/Torsten-Schwarz" target="_blank"><strong>marketingB&ouml;rse</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Marketing-B&ouml;rse&quot;''de, marketing ile ilgili, kaliteli bilgiler ve uzmanlar bulabilirsiniz.   </li></ul><blockquote> <a href="http://www.marketing-boerse.de" title="Marketingboerse - Anbieter und Agenturen rund um Marketing, IT und Vertrieb"><img src="/img/comm_icons/mabo.jpg" border="0" alt="marketingboerse-logo" /></a></blockquote><ul><li> <a href="http://www.mikestar.de" title="Mikestar"><strong>MIKESTAR</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Mikestar&quot; ile Karako-fanlar&iota; istedikleri kadar şarki s&ouml;yleme ve eğlenme imkan&iota; buluyorlar. Mikestar sizi eğlendiriyor.</li></ul><blockquote> <a href="http://www.mikestar.de" title="Mikestar"><img src="/img/comm_icons/mikestar2.jpg" border="0" alt="mikestar-logo" /></a></blockquote><ul><li> <a href="http://www.mygamersclub.com/" target="_blank"><strong>MyGamersClub</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;myGamersClub&quot; herkeze hitap eden bir Gaming-Netw&ouml;rk''&uuml;d&uuml;r.            Şimdi &uuml;ye ol, profil d&uuml;zenle ve yeni veya eski arkadaşlar&iota;n&iota; bul.</li></ul><blockquote> <a href="http://www.mygamersclub.de" title="Mygamersclub - Deutschlands Gaming-Network fuer alle"><img src="/img/comm_icons/mygamersclub.jpg" border="0" alt="mygamersclub-logo" /></a></blockquote><ul><li> <a href="http://mymusic.de/" target="_blank"><strong>MyMusic</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;mymusic&quot;''de sadece arkadaşlar&iota;nla değil, starlarla, sanat&ccedil;&iota;larla ve dj''lerle buluşabiliyorsun. Mymusic Online Music Community''lerinde bir numarad&iota;r.</li></ul><blockquote> <a href="http://www.mymusic.de" title="MyMusic"><img src="/img/comm_icons/mymusic.jpg" border="0" alt="mymusic-logo" /></a></blockquote><ul><li> <a href="http://noovee.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Noovee</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Noovee&quot;''de d&uuml;nyan&iota;n en pop&uuml;ler &uuml;lkelerinden en akt&uuml;el trendleri bulabilirsin. Noovee &ccedil;ağdaş insanlar i&ccedil;in <a href="http://www.deutsch-tuerkisch.net/suche/%C3%A7a%C4%9Fda%C5%9F"></a>uluslararas&iota; gezi ve lifestyle-portal&iota;d&iota;r. </li></ul><blockquote><a href="http://www.noovee.de" title="Noovee - my metropolitan guide"><img src="/img/comm_icons/noovee.jpg" border="0" alt="noovee-logo" /></a></blockquote> <ul><li> <a href="http://www.rhein-neckar-guide.de/" target="_blank"><strong>Rhein-Neckar-Guide</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Rhein-Neckar-Guide&quot;''da Rhein-Neckar b&ouml;lgesinde bağ&iota;ms&iota;z k&uuml;lt&uuml;r ve restoranc&iota;l&iota;k tavsiyeleri bulabilirsiniz.  </li></ul><blockquote> <a href="http://www.sixgroups.de" title="sixgroups - Kennst Du Deine Community?"><img src="/img/comm_icons/rng-logo.png" border="0" alt="sixgroups-logo" width="100" height="30" /></a></blockquote><ul><li> <a href="http://www.rnf.de/" target="_blank"><strong>RNF</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;RNF&quot;''de Rhein-Neckar b&ouml;lgesinden g&uuml;ncel haberleri bulabilirsin. RNF.de Rhein-Neckar b&ouml;lgesinde haber ve Community i&ccedil;in faydal&iota; bir plattformdur. </li></ul><blockquote><a href="http://www.rnf.de" title="Rhein-Neckar-Fernsehen"><img src="/img/comm_icons/rnf_logo.jpg" border="0" alt="rnf-logo" /></a></blockquote><blockquote> </blockquote><blockquote> </blockquote><ul><li><a href="http://de.sevenload.com/" target="_blank"><strong>Sevenload</strong></a></li></ul><blockquote> </blockquote><blockquote> </blockquote><blockquote>Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Sevenload&quot;''da videolara ve fotoğraflara bakabilirsin. Community''nin bir par&ccedil;as&iota; ol ve TV izlemenin yeni şeklini yaşa.<br /></blockquote> <blockquote><a href="http://www.sevenload.de" title="Sevenload"><img src="/img/comm_icons/sevenload.jpg" border="0" alt="sevenload-logo" /></a></blockquote> <ul><li> <a href="http://sixgroups.com/" target="_blank"><strong>sixgroups</strong></a><br />Ortağ&iota;m&iota;z &quot;Sixgroups&quot;''da bir ka&ccedil; saniye i&ccedil;inde kendi Community''ni &uuml;retibilirsin. Sixgroups &ouml;nde gelen InstantCommunity-&ccedil;&ouml;z&uuml;m&uuml;d&uuml;r.<br /> <a href="http://www.sixgroups.de" title="sixgroups - Kennst Du Deine Community?"><img src="/img/comm_icons/sixgroups.jpg" border="0" alt="sixgroups-logo" width="126" height="30" /></a> </li></ul>'),
